There isn't an installer yet. The simplest way to make it usable easily is:

Unpack it on a folder    ---> cd "folder" && tar jxvf debgui-0.0.1.tar.bz2
Make a link in /usr/bin   ---> cd /usr/bin && sudo ln -s "folder"/debgui.py debgui

Where "folder" is the folder you want.

You may use the "install.sh" script to install debgui in /usr/share/debgui
